=============================
=      File description     =
=============================

Store.java - contains an implementation of a store, managing the selling and buying of products for customers.
Customer.java - contains an implementation for customer, managing buying requested products according to balance. 
ProductType.java - contains an implementation for specific Products, defining their price for the customer and store.
README - this file


=============================
=  Implementation details   =
=============================

I implemented the classes according to the given API, while the Store class functions as the main class invoking 
the suitable methods in the Customer and ProductType classes.
